 <summary>Create and manage sitemap files.</summary>
 <description>This package allow to create sitemap files used to describe your
  website to help search engines indexing it. This package contains all needed
  functions to create, read, save, add, modify and remove url, compress to
  gzip, notify search engine and test url in the sitemap or sitemap index.
 </description>
